sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Edge Device
    participant E as Edge Management System
    participant O as System Operator
    participant A as Application Publisher
    participant C as Application Certifier<br/>(Optional)

    Note over A,C: Optional application certification activity
    A->>C: Provide publisher certificate
    A->>C: Submit application image
    C->>C: Verify publisher signature
    C->>C: Perform security review
    C->>C: Perform compatibility testing
    C-->>A: Return certification status
    C->>C: Countersign application
    C->>C: Publish certification record

    Note over O,C: Optional certifier relationship
    O->>C: Establish relationship
    C-->>O: Provide certifier certificate

